

🎯 What Your Calendar Can Do:

    ✅ Bigger calendar with large, easy-to-click dates
    📎 Attach files (drag & drop images, videos, documents)
    🏷️ Color labels to organize tasks (Work, Personal, Urgent, etc.)
    🖱️ Drag tasks between dates or reorder them
    🔔 Daily reminders with popup notifications
    💾 Saves everything in your browser automatically
    📱 Works on any device with a web browser

